section.career#career
  .grid-fluid
    .positions-apply
      h2.title Careers&nbsp;
        span We are always looking for talent
      .row
        .col-md-6.col-sm-6
          h3.title Benefits
          .content
            p Youâ€™ll have the opportunity to work on major projects with global clients. We enable continuous learning and career development,and promote from within frequently so the opportunity for career advancement is excellent. in return, we expect that you are prepared to perform at an international standard level. 
            p If you would like to join the Sutrix Media team we welcome you and encourage you to post your resume. We are always open to meeting new people and we offer competitive salaries to those that have the skills required to perform the position applied for.
        .col-md-6.col-sm-6.open-position.custom-padding
          h3.title Open positions
          .content
            ul
              li
                +link-1('PHP Developer - HCMC-Vietnam')
                  span.icon-arrow
              li
                +link-1('QC - HCMC-Vietnam')
                  span.icon-arrow
              li
                +link-1('Front-ent Developer - HCMC-Vietnam')
                  span.icon-arrow
              li
                +link-1('Java Developer')
                  span.icon-arrow
              li
                +link-1('Project Manager')
                  span.icon-arrow
            .ajax-overlay.hide
              +img('../images/ajax_loader.gif')
    .positions-detail
      .row
        .col-md-6.col-sm-6.max-height
          h3.title PHP Developer - HCMC-Vietnam
          .content
            dl
              dt Position
              dd PHP Developer
              dt Location
              dd HCMC-Vietnam
              dt Responsibilities
              dd
                p Design and write high-performance, reliable and maintainable PHP code. Be able to design and build high quality user interfaces. Work as part of a team across a wide range of projects to create innovative web applications.
              dt Requirements
              dd
                p A university degree in Computer Science or a related discipline is required. At least 2 year experience programming in PHP and familiarity with Wordpress, Joomla and Drupal. Knowledge of e-commerce workflow and issues is a plus.
        .col-md-6.col-sm-6.custom-padding
          h3.title Post your resume
          .content
            form(action='', method='post', novalidate, name='resumeform').form-1.resume-form#resume-form
              .row
                .col-md-6.col-sm-6
                  .form-group
                    label Name
                      span.orange *
                    +input('text', 'username', '', 'username')
                    span.error-message.hide Please enter your first name
                  .form-group
                    label Last name
                      span.orange *
                    +input('text', 'lastname', '', 'lastname')
                    span.error-message.hide Please enter your last name
                  .form-group
                    label Email
                      span.orange *
                    +input('text', 'email', '', 'email')
                    span.error-message.hide Please enter email address
                  .form-group
                    label Upload CV
                      span.orange *
                    .upload
                      +input('file', 'file')
                      +input('text', 'upload', '', 'upload')
                      span.bgd-orange Browse
                    span.error-message.hide Please select your resume
                .col-md-6.col-sm-6
                  .form-group
                    label Comments
                      span.orange *
                    textarea(id="comment", name='comment')
                  .form-group.capcha
                    label Security images
                      span.orange *
                    .field-capcha
                      +img('../images/photo-capcha.jpg', '')
                    .field-security
                      +input('text', 'security', '', 'security')
                      span.error-message.hide Please enter code
                  .form-group
                    button(type="submit", name="submit").send-btn.btn.btn-color
                      span Send
                    button(type="button", name="").send-btn.btn.btn-color.clear-btn
                      span Clear
      button(type="button", name="back").back-btn.btn.btn-color
        span Back
